<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary concerned and the Secretary of Veterans Affairs shall prescribe regulations necessary to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb0b6e0a1-2930-11f1-a69d-9cbca84c43f0">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/649">Pub. L. 87–649</ref>, <date date="1962-09-07">Sept. 7, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/484">76 Stat. 484</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/189/dA/tXVI/s1621/b/2">Pub. L. 101–189, div. A, title XVI, § 1621(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="1989-11-29">Nov. 29, 1989</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/103/1604">103 Stat. 1604</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
